  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy Pilot Study of AzaSite速 (Azithromycin) in Subjects With Blepharitis</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multi-Center, Open-Label, Randomized Pilot Study of the Safety and Efficacy of AzaSite速 Ophthalmic Solution, 1% in Combination With Mechanical Therapy Versus Mechanical Therapy Alone in Subjects With Blepharitis</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Merck Sharp &amp; Dohme Corp.</agency>
      <agency_class>Industry</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Merck Sharp &amp; Dohme Corp.</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the safety and efficacy of AzaSite速 ophthalmic
      solution, 1% on signs and symptoms of blepharitis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
